            </td>
        </tr><tr><td><img width="500" height="346" src="http://img2.news.zing.vn/2012/09/13/h2-1.jpg" alt="&#7842;nh 'photoshop' &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i m&#7851;u n&#7897;i y th&#7871; k&#7927; tr&#432;&#7899;c" class="oImage" style="border: 0px; text-align: middle;" /></td>
